{"tid":1787577,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"青衣/荃灣區電結他招生, 教jazz亦教rock2","createTime":"2019-12-18T04:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:54:41.000Z","uid":166708,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd81c00cb305838ed08f6f8e2a0f2bb94eecbba","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"Hello, 本身打算今年年尾 個學生份8級出埋先 開新POST<br />\n<br />\n不過Rockschool delay 左...咁打左D 一步步練上去結他彈五線譜教學,順便係度分享<br />\n<br />\n呢三份五級CERT係3~5月 , 當中有兩個學生係度招...大約學左一年...<br />\n<br />\n佢地本身連4分音符都行唔直...對唔個TRACK , 一年狂操拍子,JAMMING 同唔同風格solo寫法<br />\n<br />\n個考試雖然唔算難,可以話係幾易,不過其實要寫好段SOLO 都幾過癮同埋操到個學生一拍都唔甩<br />\n<br />\n都幾有成就感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsiUdZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsiUdZG.jpg&h=d6ce7a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多年教結他經驗,有學生已經做老師<br />\n<br />\n會教cover, jamming ,solo build up,各種style 同五線譜, 亦會有jazz standard , duo 咁教<br />\n<br />\nJazz 果邊會解唔同情景, 例如III7 用harmonic minor,轉調的SOLO 處理,alter scales ,dorian 的運用<br />\n會講點用同比住licks 學<br />\n<br />\n資歷: rockschool 8級電結他, 5級皇家鋼琴,五級樂理 地點: 青衣/荃灣<br />\n<br />\n實戰: 4年爵士大樂團, 一年兒童合唱團, jazz band 同各大大小小的酒店演出<br />\n<br />\n教學經驗: 2015 年 poly 音樂比賽冠軍 (份譜係我幫個學生編,幫佢執左個BASS,結他同鼓)<br />\n<br />\n聽個學生講佢地攞冠軍之後畀紅線簽咗約<br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法: Tg :klguitar (第一堂試堂免費)"},{"pid":"e2f9d73c082c3a46002088dd0a8e20298e8a1d21","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"1. 結他睇五線譜要熟三大範疇<br />\n<br />\n一: 五線譜本身要識睇<br />\n<br />\n二: 結他指板<br />\n<br />\n三: 結他指板同五線譜的關係<br />\n<br />\n咁睇五線譜之前就一定要講下調性<br />\n<br />\n咁調性就要開兩個篇章去講<br />\n<br />\n調性第一章:<br />\n<br />\n其實十二個主調或者音樂最開始係用一個稱為Major scale 的東西去建立<br />\n<br />\n最簡單的理解就係<br />\n<br />\nDo re mi fa so la ti do' 去建立音樂<br />\n<br />\n而點解有呢堆音去形成 DO去 高8度DO (一個重疊的音軌)<br />\n<br />\n背後就有個偉大的物理學家去定立十二平衡律<br />\n<br />\n十二平衡律可以理解為音樂的十二元色/十二進制,分別係<br />\n<br />\n(#)<br />\n<br />\nC C# D D# E F F# G G# A A# B C'<br />\n<br />\n(b)<br />\n<br />\nC Db D Eb E F Gb G Ab A Bb B C'<br />\n<br />\n# 為高半度,結他向右一格<br />\n<br />\nB 為低半度,結他向左一格<br />\n<br />\n咁呢堆野FIX 死左的, 因為個物理學家發現C 去 高8度C 如果SET 做呢十二進階就可以係一個重疊的音色<br />\n<br />\n咁樣西方音樂就開始建立起來,基本上的西方樂理都係用十二平均律去製造樂器<br />\n<br />\n咁有左十二平衡律之後就有個神人叫巴哈再發展左十二個調<br />\n<br />\n姐係上面用Do re mi fa so la ti do' 的方法去造左十二個調(下稱major scale)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁Major scale 入面有咩需要理解去發展成調性呢<br />\n<br />\n就係網上/教科書常講的<br />\n<br />\n全全半全全全半 / 2 2 1 2 2 2 1<br />\n<br />\n全可理解為兩個半度, 結他向右兩格<br />\n<br />\n半可理解為一個半度,結他向左一格<br />\n<br />\n將Do re mi fa so la ti do 套入去,就會得出下表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TsJRMy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TsJRMy.png&h=a2807024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢個音程就係我地音樂堂想講的do re mi fa so la ti do'(major scale)<br />\n<br />\n十二個調可以理解為個Do 係邊粒音行先就係果個major scale<br />\n<br />\n(C key)(Start with C)(All natural)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNSRgdj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNSRgdj.png&h=82dcaf10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單來講就係 MI-&gt; FA 同Ti -&gt;Do 都為半度<br />\n<br />\n其他都為全度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n**進階諗法: 非全全半全全全半 / 2 2 1 2 2 2 1的音階就不能組成major scale<br />\n<br />\n下篇會有其他key 作對照同埋比大家一個極方便的省略法去記"},{"pid":"aad73157bfef56d8548a2b2b0a8a029def308ec5","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"講完12 平均律<br />\n而家講點樣去記調性<br />\n<br />\n調性有分# 同b<br />\n# 為高半度， 結他向右行一格<br />\nb 為低半度， 結他向左行一格<br />\n<br />\n咁記key 有個好好的口訣<br />\nGo Down And Eat breakfast<br />\n分別係：<br />\n1 個# 為G ; 2個# 為D ; 3 個# 為A<br />\n如此類推<br />\n<br />\n咁我地攤開三條key來睇就更清晰<br />\nG(F#)<br />\nG A B C D E F# G<br />\n<br />\nD(F#,C#)<br />\nD E F# G A B C# D<br />\n<br />\nA(F# C# G#)<br />\nA B C# D E F# G# A<br />\n<br />\n你會睇到口訣係幫到我地知邊條key有幾多個#<br />\n但仍要慢慢推敲邊粒音<br />\n<br />\n咁我有個好好的方法幫大家記<br />\n<br />\n就係每#條key都係繼承上條key再加自己key的7 音<br />\n<br />\nG key的 7 音為F ;<br />\n所以 G為 (F#)<br />\n<br />\nD key 繼承上條key 的F# ,<br />\n7 音為C ; 所以D為(F#,C#)<br />\n<br />\nA key 繼承上條key的 F# C# ,<br />\n7 音為 G 所以A為( F#, C#,G# )<br />\n<br />\n咁用呢個方法就可以key 與key之間記得有聯繫<br />\n而且可以唔洗數2212221 數到傻<br />\nE( F# C# G# D#)<br />\nB( F# C# G# D# A#)"},{"pid":"c38225c65abf51ee2314af878c32b29053a80097","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"上面講完# key<br />\n而家講b key (Flat)<br />\nFlat 為低半度， 格他向左一格就係flat 半度<br />\n<br />\n口訣為：<br />\nFat Boy Eat All Day<br />\n除左f key (Bb)之外<br />\nB E A D分別都要加個b<br />\nBb, Eb , Ab, Db<br />\n<br />\nF為 1 個flat ; Bb 為2 個flat ; Eb為3 個flat<br />\n如此類推<br />\n<br />\n佢地同# 唔同, 每個flat key都為4 音flat<br />\n一樣繼承上條key<br />\n<br />\n拎三條來印證<br />\nF(Bb)<br />\nF G A Bb C D E F<br />\n<br />\nBb (Bb, Eb)<br />\nBb C D Eb F G A Bb<br />\n<br />\nEb(Bb, Eb, Ab)<br />\nEb F G Ab Bb C D Eb<br />\n<br />\n你會見到佢地教係繼承上一條key 的flat note<br />\n再憑4 音加新一條key 的flat"},{"pid":"3c8065acace4cd716af8501f711fe9bca55552e8","tid":1787577,"uid":156173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"講解得好"},{"pid":"e5a8a793efcba5eecbc4ef41d7e93832dbfa26d9","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c8065acace4cd716af8501f711fe9bca55552e8","tid":1787577,"uid":156173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"講解得好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"多謝多謝 會繼續慢慢寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858a2760336752148f0f0e69ffa79364a3ffe8a9","tid":1787577,"uid":217478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73268ae3c33e9c3975e2b66c31a41ecbee986c4","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"858a2760336752148f0f0e69ffa79364a3ffe8a9","tid":1787577,"uid":217478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208379de679120a4fecf98d742232141cbdd17ed","tid":1787577,"uid":254546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6b78acc1abb949fa1a3195493c2541c9d3d960a9","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"各位聖誕快樂 過幾日出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e7e00c80c50898f16b72fe8e00b6981fbd80f7","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:11:47.000Z","msg":"Scale 的理解同應用 1<br />\n<br />\n我地講完樂理部分,去到實戰,去番結他指板部分<br />\n<br />\n第一套scale 的指板建議練下邊呢條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQC0hRp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQC0hRp.png&h=ff869578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁同學們會問,個指板點用<br />\n<br />\n首先我要彈scale, 要假定key 先<br />\n<br />\nKey (調性共十二條) 唔明可以問亦可以睇番上面<br />\n<br />\n我地假定左C Key (Major scale) 先<br />\n<br />\n就會得出下面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kS7Hjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kS7Hjp.png&h=30c9dda4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n橙色圖圈為Do, 結他思維慣性用個正方框去背個指板手法<br />\n<br />\n咁3弦第五格為C 音, 跟住上面個指法就會套用番<br />\n<br />\n(沿伸思考, 你將3弦第7格的D 音變Do, 成套指法跟住變就變Dkey)<br />\n<br />\n(下篇會講轉調)<br />\n<br />\nCKey <br />\nDo :C      Re: D<br />\n<br />\nMi: E      Fa: F<br />\n<br />\nSo: G      La: A<br />\n<br />\nTi: B<br />\n<br />\n咁想行多兩步的同學可以係結他指板逐粒逐粒音對<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前學結他,練指板就好悶的,之後跟過一個勁的老師佢就話熟一條Scale 最好就執歌執番來<br />\n<br />\n因為執歌就要用,用就迫住熟<br />\n<br />\n例子: So, mi mi , Fa re re, Do re mi fa so so so , So, mi mi , fa re re, mi so, re mi do<br />\n<br />\n假設我番琴行番工聽到鋼琴老師教呢首兒歌,咁我聽到番上面呢堆音碼<br />\n<br />\n熟指板的要馬上可以Load 番做下表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYgDO0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYgDO0a.png&h=0243e6ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果可以就係你係街諗Solo的時侯, 諗完一堆音之後, 可以唔洗用結他的情況係腦度行一次你運行緊的野<br />\n<br />\n做到呢個程度就叫熟悉條Scale"},{"pid":"a10a24802b9e9916e192b3126be958deeaf39f8a","tid":1787577,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"係香港玩結他既係咪除左教結他就無其他相關行業可以維生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debb1f22d757906f031909f1de95188f5a439265","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a10a24802b9e9916e192b3126be958deeaf39f8a","tid":1787577,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"係香港玩結他既係咪除左教結他就無其他相關行業可以維生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"唉 出去彈野 / 彈合唱團都係得好雞錢<br />\n<br />\n付出時多 ， 收獲低<br />\n<br />\n除非跟到大佬 做演唱會<br />\n<br />\n不過做空中飛人 唔係個個想呢種生活<br />\n<br />\n所以結果都係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你懂的"},{"pid":"3153ea2c04a44274ae14f39969eebdad1e847d61","tid":1787577,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"debb1f22d757906f031909f1de95188f5a439265","tid":1787577,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a10a24802b9e9916e192b3126be958deeaf39f8a","tid":1787577,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:24:34.0